properties.Description:
Come together with friends, family, and neighbors to call voters in support of Bernie! Phonebanking is one of *the most important things* you can do to help our campaign win. Every call helps us grow our movement, turn Bernie supporters out to vote, and win this election in a landslide.

**Note:** In addition to a cell phone, please bring a laptop or tablet to use to make calls on the Bernie Dialer. I have a few extra computers /tablets as well, do if you do not have a laptop still come to help.

Reúnase con sus amigos, familiares y vecinos para llamar a votantes y pedirles que se unan a nuestra campaña histórica para derrotar a Trump y transformar a los Estados Unidos. Juntos, hablaremos con nuestros vecinos y tendremos conversaciones importantes en una elección tan importante como esta.

properties.Title: Bernie 2020 Phonebank in Denver
properties.Description:
EVERY MONDAY NIGHT: Come together at our collective house with your friends, family, and neighbors to call voters and ask them to join our historic campaign to defeat Trump and transform America. BYOB and snacks if desired.

Note: In addition to a cell phone, please bring a laptop or tablet to use to make calls on the Bernie Dialer.
